etamine and ethanol interactions in humans." Clin Pharmacol Ther 57 (1995): 559-68[7] Jiao X, Velez S, Ringstad J, Eyma V, Miller D, Bleiberg M "Myocardial infarction associated with Adderall XR and alcohol use in a young man." J Am Board Fam Med 22 (2009): 197-201', 1767365206);
